@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

# ❗固定一次随机种子，别用 {{$timestamp}}，避免登录时变成新邮箱
# 想换一批测试账号，只需要手动改这个数字即可
@rnd = 1730080000

# 用同一个邮箱跑 “注册 -> 登录”
@email = dev{{rnd}}@mx.com
@password = Passw0rd!

### 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### 注册（先跑这条；若返回 409，说明已注册过，直接跳“登录”）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "fifi",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "role": "student"
}

### 登录（必须与上面的 email/password 完全一致）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}
